{"tid":252701,"cid":8,"subCid":0,"title":"兩套災難漫 變成王道漫","createTime":"2017-05-21T19:50:26.000Z","updateTime":"2017-05-23T09:55:51.000Z","uid":90520,"like":0,"dislike":0,"uniUserReply":0,"replies":[{"pid":"c6c5bff2ce14831bceffc6e0bab1a1ef074f50a0","tid":252701,"uid":90520,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2017-05-21T19:50:26.000Z","msg":"相信大家都估到邊套<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/dead.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /> <br />\n<span style=\"font-size: x-large;\">破壞獸</span><br />\n同<br />\n<span style=\"font-size: x-large;\">玩偶殺人遊戲</span><br />\n<br />\n兩套本來都好好地<br />\n講緊 人類幾咁絕望 乜都做唔到<br />\n只可以為生存而生存<br />\n<br />\n路人主角冇啦啦 上撚哂身<br />\n一個就話啲基因好撚fit<br />\n一個就講原來同個boss係同種<br />\n<br />\n完全冇伏筆 冇鋪過<br />\n突然轉變 完全唔知做乜尻<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/dead.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /> <br />\n<br />\n<br />\n雖然我都會繼續追<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/clown.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"48489424d0b6ba03904757371dd9be07da597f89","tid":252701,"uid":8307,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2017-05-21T19:51:26.000Z","msg":"災難漫畫變超能力打鬥好似都好常見<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/sosad.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"282adb63d9fc2fbe998584b3048ae0f232670b45","tid":252701,"uid":90520,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2017-05-21T19:52:41.000Z","msg":"<blockquote>災難漫畫變超能力打鬥好似都好常見<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/sosad.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /></blockquote><br />\n兩套 成個路線其實一樣<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/dead.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /> <br />\n<span style=\"font-size: xx-large;\">冇分別</span>"},{"pid":"5b8e987abc910946aff6e7764e182320ca042b1c","tid":252701,"uid":51300,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2017-05-21T22:13:37.000Z","msg":"分分鐘係前面D災難根本唔好睇，冇咩人氣結果諗住順勢轉王道點知結果死得仲慘。"},{"pid":"90954c0c7844741c7ea399215339f7eacc14efb7","tid":252701,"uid":96128,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2017-05-22T00:38:01.000Z","msg":"好想知破壞獸點收尾 老師發癲上黎佢一個都可以殺哂所有人類<br />\n第二套照劇情睇可能打贏左雪佳 人偶就無哂咁完？"},{"pid":"8d7ad0794c